commit message: Import JitterBuffer related classes adapted from mobicents
Create separate RX thread to receive network traffice and populate jitter buffer
Move DNS SRV helper code to opentelecoms.org-util
Use correct timestamp ratio in AudioClock
Rename Java namespace from zorg to org.opentelecoms.media.rtp.secure
Remove patch to use JitterBuffer for RtpStreamReceiver
Eliminate SIP stack dependencies on the UA code by subclassing SipProvider
SIP TLS support: re-register after re-connect, as for TCP
Add preference for forcing speakerphone mode on all calls
Fix ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException when adding SIP account
Handle missing username when creating contact URL
Show a popup error for some types of call failure
Allow user to choose SIP identity when dialing from main screen
